Selepas menghapuskan penanam gelap,

00:12:50.204 --> 00:12:50.885
apabila Tuan Muda

00:12:50.885 --> 00:12:51.844
memimpin murid baru,

00:12:51.844 --> 00:12:53.245
Saya akan bermain dengan mereka setiap hari.

00:12:53.724 --> 00:12:56.005
Harapan yang mudah.

00:12:56.165 --> 00:12:56.844
Ingin?

00:12:57.125 --> 00:12:59.045
Bercakap tentang keinginan, saya mempunyai satu.

00:12:59.072 --> 00:13:00.804
Apa itu? Bolehkah anda berkongsi?

00:13:00.844 --> 00:13:01.765
ia...

00:13:03.724 --> 00:13:05.365
Ludahkan atau jangan!

00:13:05.365 --> 00:13:07.125
baiklah! Saya akan mengatakannya.

00:13:09.005 --> 00:13:10.604
Hasrat saya ialah

00:13:10.765 --> 00:13:13.216
untuk mencari rakan penanaman

00:13:13.525 --> 00:13:15.136
yang berkongsi minat saya.

00:13:15.444 --> 00:13:17.344
Dan kami akan membesarkan anak bersama-sama

00:13:17.684 --> 00:13:18.724
dan memelihara seekor anjing.

00:13:18.924 --> 00:13:20.324
Sama ada kita naik

00:13:20.485 --> 00:13:21.792
atau kekal di Alam Lingyou,

00:13:22.245 --> 00:13:23.072
kita akan

00:13:23.365 --> 00:13:24.964
hidup bahagia seperti abadi.

00:13:27.045 --> 00:13:29.165
Musang mahukan isteri!

00:13:29.285 --> 00:13:31.645
Sayang sekali. Tiada siapa yang mahu musang busuk.

00:13:32.324 --> 00:13:33.765
K-Kau pelita bodoh!

00:13:33.885 --> 00:13:35.165
Oh, saya faham!

00:13:35.365 --> 00:13:36.724
Anda mahu Ling Bo

00:13:36.724 --> 00:13:38.285
untuk mengahwini awak.

00:13:39.084 --> 00:13:39.684
senyap!

00:13:40.005 --> 00:13:40.844
mengarut!

00:13:41.765 --> 00:13:43.204
S-Ia hanya bercakap kosong.

00:13:45.245 --> 00:13:45.924
Jadi awak...

00:13:45.924 --> 00:13:47.405
Tidakkah anda fikir idea saya ini

00:13:47.405 --> 00:13:48.365
adalah sempurna?

00:13:49.204 --> 00:13:50.045
Itu sahaja?

00:13:50.204 --> 00:13:50.924
Itu sahaja.

00:13:50.924 --> 00:13:51.684
Sempurna?

00:13:51.844 --> 00:13:52.485
Tidak sempurna?

00:13:52.604 --> 00:13:53.645
Klise!

00:13:54.285 --> 00:13:55.324
Seorang lelaki dewasa

00:13:55.324 --> 00:13:56.005
menghabiskan sepanjang hari

00:13:56.005 --> 00:13:57.324
obses dengan cinta.

00:13:57.405 --> 00:13:58.444
Tunggu. Apa maksud awak

00:13:58.444 --> 00:13:59.844
"lelaki dewasa yang obses dengan cinta?"

